I’m so excited to share with you @shftbeauty! I can’t wait for you guys to get your hands on my Eyebrow Kits today at 5pm PST on @whatnot! Be sure to tune in for some cool surprises, giveaways, to hear my story and get up close and personal with my brows! 

For over a decade you all have made my brows Insta-famous since my first selfie! I’ve traveled the world teaching lash and brow masterclasses and I’ll never forget about all the people that has supported me through the years like the mother who flew all the way to the Gold Coast in Australia to take my brow class for her daughter because she could not attend. I knew from that day this day would come. My brows have been my #1 requested tutorial and I’ve simplified my steps into two amazing products so that you can easily achieve my signature Ombré Powder Brow look! This drop is for you all! Xx
I promise you will love it. @shftbeauty #shftgirls
Fresh Brow Friday! Wearing my Eyebrow Kit 02! @shftbeauty #shftgirls

I launched @shftbeauty as a farewell to the tedious and nerve-wracking ordeal of putting on makeup. It should be a party, a moment that unleashes your inner rockstar! Our mission is to celebrate your natural beauty, not hide it behind a mask. #shftbeauty #shftgirls
